// ------------------------------------------------------------

16. CBC bit flipping

See cbcFlip.py

It works because CBC decrypts by XORing the ciphertext of the previous
block against the decrypted text of the current block. So changing the
ciphertext of one block will only affect the decryption of the next
block.

